{"tid":121880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 突發】公民黨通過提名胡國興或曾俊華","createTime":"2017-02-15T14:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T14:47:19.000Z","uid":35519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36ee26b4df62f7f1720b3aac005d19a6c0f15528","tid":121880,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivicpartyhk%2F&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ec8e57e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨執委會通過的提名策略如下:<br />\n<br />\n基於締造競爭，抗衡西環操控的原則，公民黨會配合「民主300+」分工合作的策略，即使胡國興，曾俊華的政綱未完全符合民主派理念，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公民黨決定，本黨選委將提名胡國興或曾俊華</span></strong>; 亦有部份選委會等待公民提名結果再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公民黨的特首選舉提名與投票策略分開處理，現階段，先處理提名策略。</span><br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"84d8ee992c75b065c39a52c2562d26afe6a288b1","tid":121880,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"戴生個公民提名俾私隱專員公署秒左喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}